Class Computer

  • java.lang.Object
    • Computer

  • public class Computer
extends java.lang.Object

    Computer Generator

    Version:
    0.2.2

    A simple class used to fill in the specs for a computer.

    Contains several functions that can be used print the specs or to write it to a file
    Author:
    Gibson Holben
